metadata.name: Dreamer
metadata.description: She loved to fly in the clouds. Every time she closed her eyes, she was transported to a beautiful World. A world where there were several moons in the sky. A world where everyone was happy. A world where there were no resentments and envy. A world where there were no wars and no knowledge of pain. A perfect World. With her faithful sidekick Pete they rode her pink moped all over the world, counting the stars and moons, playing her keychain bear and purring a song to herself under her nose she was happy. Her name was Avril.
